I wait for element {xpath: .//div[@class = 'dx-overlay dx-widget dx-visibility-change-handler dx-loadpanel dx-state-invisible']}, 60
I wait for visible {xpath: .//span[contains(., 'Yes')][ancestor::*[contains(concat(' ', normalize-space(./@class), ' '), ' dx-popup-content ')]]}, 20
I wait for visible {xpath: .//*[contains(concat(' ', normalize-space(./@class), ' '), ' jq-icon-success ')][ancestor::*[contains(concat(' ', normalize-space(./@class), ' '), ' jq-toast-wrap ')]]}, 60

I wait for clickable {xpath: .//*[contains(concat(' ', normalize-space(./@class), ' '), ' jq-icon-success ')][ancestor::*[contains(concat(' ', normalize-space(./@class), ' '), ' jq-toast-wrap ')]]}, 20

I wait for invisible {xpath: .//*[contains(concat(' ', normalize-space(./@class), ' '), ' jq-icon-success ')][ancestor::*[contains(concat(' ', normalize-space(./@class), ' '), ' jq-toast-wrap ')]]}, 20
I wait for element {xpath: .//div[@class = 'dx-overlay dx-widget dx-visibility-change-handler dx-loadpanel']}, 20
I wait for element {xpath: .//div[@class = 'dx-overlay dx-widget dx-visibility-change-handler dx-loadpanel dx-state-invisible']}, 60
I see element {xpath: .//span[@id = 'Message_Task_Cancelled'][contains(., 'The task was cancelled due to a related approval task being rejected or returned.')]}
